# DEPRECATED FILES

The following files in the root directory are deprecated and kept for reference only:
- app.js (1075 lines) - Replaced by modular src/ structure
- server.js (256 lines) - Replaced by server/index.js and route files
- db.js (301 lines) - Replaced by server/db/ structure

## New Structure
All new development should use:
- Backend: server/ directory (routes, middleware, db models)
- Frontend: src/ directory (views, components, router, store)
- Static files: public/ directory

See README.md for complete project structure and setup instructions.
